{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"title","type":"text","text":"# Claude Code 完整架构图谱\n**非官方学习仓库** - 结合 miaomiaomiao1113 架构分析 + 本地部署实践\n\n涵盖：终端输入 → 命令分发 → 环境感知 → 上下文压缩 → 大模型推理 → 工具执行 → 多轮对话 → 记忆保存","x":-100,"y":-1600,"width":600,"height":120,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"e2e-ref","type":"text","text":"## 端到端流程参考\n- [[end_to_end_workflow.md]] - 七大阶段完整时序\n- [[harness_engine_architecture.md]] - 宿主工程全景\n- [[compact_architecture.md]] - 三级防爆体系","x":-100,"y":-1460,"width":600,"height":100,"color":"0"},
		{"id":"user-input","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 1：用户终端输入\n\n在终端敲下指令并回车\n\n**触发方式**：stdin / Ink TUI 事件","x":0,"y":-1200,"width":280,"height":100,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"phase1","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 1：终端接收与命令分发\n`entrypoints/cli.tsx` & `commands/`\n\n**CLI 解析**：\n- commander/yargs 命令行解析\n- `preflightChecks.tsx` 预检探针\n  - Node.js 版本检查\n  - 执行权限验证\n  - 更新检测\n- 斜杠命令本地拦截\n  - `/compact` → 直接执行\n  - `/clear` → 本地清理\n  - `/stop` → 中断当前请求\n- 普通对话 → 流转至 QueryEngine\n\n**Fast-path 短路**：`--version` / `--help` / `daemon`","x":-60,"y":-1000,"width":450,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"entrypoint-module","type":"text","text":"# entrypoint 入口引导链\n`entrypoints/`\n\n**核心职责**：\n- CLI 解析器初始化\n- CWD 感知 & Settings 加载\n- Session 恢复 & Auth 鉴权\n- React Ink TUI 渲染宿主初始化\n- 引擎交接 → QueryEngine\n\n**文件清单**：\n- `cli.tsx` - CLI 主入口\n- `init.ts` - 系统初始化\n- `main.tsx` - 主循环\n- `mcp.ts` - MCP 服务器","x":-600,"y":-1000,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"phase2","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 2：环境感知与物理世界挂载\n`context.ts` & `QueryEngine.ts`\n\n**环境注射**：\n- `getGitStatus()` - 并发抓取 4 条 git 命令\n  - git branch / git status\n  - git log / git config user.name\n- 超 2000 字符强制截断防污染\n- `memoize` 防止重复扫描\n\n**上下文注入**：\n- 本地时间戳（防幻觉）\n- 项目 `CLAUDE.md` 知识库\n- 系统上下文 + 缓存击穿\n\n**账单追踪**：\n- UUID 标记请求\n- Token 用量统计\n- 美元账单累加","x":-60,"y":-640,"width":450,"height":280,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"query-engine","type":"text","text":"# QueryEngine.ts - 会话总调度室\n\n**核心状态**：\n- `mutableMessages` - 完整对话数组\n- `submitMessage()` - 统一 AsyncGenerator 入口\n\n**职责**：\n- Token 用量统计 / 美元账单累加\n- `maxBudgetUsd` 预算上限斩断\n- `recordTranscript` 多卡点持久化\n- `abortController` 实例级中断\n- 斜杠命令伪装成 AI 回复\n\n**文件位置**：`src/services/QueryEngine.ts`","x":500,"y":-640,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"context-module","type":"text","text":"# context.ts - 世界观注射站\n\n**函数清单**：\n- `getGitStatus()` - git 状态并发抓取\n- `getUserContext()` - 日期 + CLAUDE.md\n- `getSystemContext()` - git 状态 + 缓存\n- `memoize()` - 防止重复扫描\n\n**设计意图**：\n冷启动注射：先喂环境，省一个 RoundTrip\n\n**详见**：[[context_architecture.md]]","x":900,"y":-640,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"phase3","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 3：提示词预检与缓存折叠\n`compact/` 三级防爆体系\n\n**第一级** `microCompact.ts`\n- 时间断层清理旧工具结果\n- Cache Edits 无损编辑\n- 删除旧工具超长结果\n\n**第二级** `sessionMemoryCompact.ts`\n- 读取 SESSION_MEMORY.md\n- 0 延迟注射，不发 API 请求\n- `calculateMessagesToKeepIndex` 精准切割\n\n**第三级** `compact.ts` (Legacy)\n- 单独长调用强制生成\n- `<compacted_summary>` 推倒重来","x":-60,"y":-240,"width":450,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"compact-module","type":"text","text":"# compact/ - 三级防爆体系\n\n**设计哲学**：阶梯式防御\n\n**文件清单**：\n- `microCompact.ts` - 微观清理\n- `sessionMemoryCompact.ts` - 会话摘要\n- `compact.ts` - 终极压缩\n- `autoCompact.ts` - 自动触发\n\n**触发条件**：\n- Token 接近上限\n- 用户显式调用 `/compact`\n- 后台自动检测","x":-600,"y":-240,"width":350,"height":260,"color":"2"},
		{"id":"session-memory","type":"text","text":"# SessionMemory - 会话级临时记忆\n\n**触发条件** `shouldExtractMemory()`：\n- 容量阈值 `hasMetUpdateThreshold`\n- 动作阈值 `hasMetToolCallThreshold`\n- 自然间隙 `!hasToolCallsInLastTurn`\n\n**隔离执行**：\n- `createSubagentContext` 环境隔离\n- `runForkedAgent` 派生独立人格\n- `createMemoryFileCanUseTool` 权限锁死\n\n**产出**：SESSION_MEMORY.md\n**供 compact 第二级复用**\n\n**详见**：[[sessionMemory_architecture.md]]","x":-1100,"y":-240,"width":350,"height":260,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"phase4","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 4：大模型推理主循环\n`query.ts` : `queryLoop`\n\n**流式生成器**：\n- `async function*` 流式输出\n- `while(true)` 无限状态机循环\n- 流式 Streaming 逐字 yield 给终端\n\n**处理分支**：\n- text → 即时渲染给终端\n- tool_use → 发起工具调用\n- end_turn → 宣布完结\n\n**韧性设计**：\n- 超 Token 自动续写（无损拼接 8K+）\n- Error Recovery 自愈式\n- Fallback Model 降级重试","x":-60,"y":140,"width":450,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"query-engine-core","type":"text","text":"# query.ts - 流式状态机（发动机）\n\n**核心循环**：\n- `async function*` 流式生成器\n- `while(true)` 无限状态机\n- `checkTokenBudget()` 预算追踪\n\n**处理逻辑**：\n- 流式 Streaming 逐字 yield\n- tool_use → 工具分发\n- tool_result → 回填再循环\n- 超 Token 自动续写\n\n**详见**：[[query_architecture.md]]","x":-600,"y":140,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"3"},
		{"id":"phase5","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 5：工具审查与沙盒执行\n`Tool.ts` / Permissions / MCP\n\n**工具调用流程**：\n1. `inputSchema` Zod 参数验证\n2. `isDestructive()` 破坏性标记\n3. `checkPermissions()` 运行时拦截\n\n**权限路由**：\n- YOLO 模式自动放行\n- allow / deny / ask 三级决策\n- `yoloClassifier` 语义风险打分\n\n**执行结果**：\n- 沙盒执行：安全操作直接运行\n- 失败自愈：报错文本反馈给 Agent 重试\n- MCP 外部工具协议兼容","x":-60,"y":500,"width":450,"height":280,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"tool-system","type":"text","text":"# Tool.ts - 工具插槽系统\n\n**核心接口**：\n- `inputSchema` - Zod 参数声明\n- `description()` - system prompt 注入\n- `isDestructive()` - 破坏性标记\n- `isReadOnly()` / `isConcurrencySafe()`\n- `checkPermissions()` - 运行时拦截\n- `renderToolUseMessage()` - UI 渲染钩子\n- `buildTool()` - 工厂默认值填充\n\n**内置工具**：\n- Read/Write/Edit/Glob/Grep/Bash\n- Agent/MCP/Skill 工具","x":-1100,"y":500,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"permissions-module","type":"text","text":"# Permissions - 权限路由引擎\n\n**文件清单**：\n- `permissionsLoader.ts` - 规则加载\n- `permissionRuleParser.ts` - 特征匹配\n- `yoloClassifier.ts` - 语义风险打分\n\n**决策流程**：\n1. 静态扫描风险特征\n2. 轻量模型推断\n3. allow / deny / ask 三级决策\n4. 紧急刹车安全网\n\n**详见**：[[permissions_architecture.md]]","x":-1550,"y":500,"width":350,"height":280,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"mcp-module","type":"text","text":"# MCP 协议层\nModel Context Protocol\n\n**连接模式**：\n- STDIO / HTTP SSE 双连接\n- `initialize` 握手获取 capabilities\n\n**功能映射**：\n- `tools/list` → 原生 Tool 插槽\n- Prompts 聚合 & Resources 读取\n- JSON-RPC 流水线 & 超时容错\n\n**详见**：[[mcp_architecture.md]]","x":-1550,"y":850,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"phase6","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 6：多轮缠斗与主动完结\n\n**循环条件**：\n- tool_result 返回 → 携新结果再次循环\n- 模型递归思考直到信息足够\n\n**完结条件**：\n- `stop_reason: end_turn` → 宣布完结\n- 用户主动 Ctrl+C 中断\n\n**追问机制**：\n- 需要更多信息 → 重入循环\n- 任务完成 → 输出最终响应","x":500,"y":500,"width":350,"height":200,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"phase7","type":"text","text":"# 阶段 7：背景幽灵善后\nPost Sampling Hooks\n\n**触发时机**：\n- 主屏静止后后台触发\n- `handleStopHooks` 独立管线\n\n**执行内容**：\n- Fork 纯净分身子代理\n- 后台记忆总结\n- 结果互不干扰主线程\n\n**宽限期**：\n- Ctrl+C 后 60 秒确保写完","x":-60,"y":900,"width":450,"height":200,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"extract-memories","type":"text","text":"# ExtractMemories - 长期跨会话记忆\n\n**触发方式** `handleStopHooks`：\n- `turnsSinceLastExtraction` 节流\n- `hasMemoryWritesSince` 互斥检查\n\n**闭包状态机** `initExtractMemories()`：\n- `inProgress` / `pendingContext` 合并\n- 尾随提取（trailing run）不漏看\n\n**产出**：\n- 内容卡片 `.md` (YAML Frontmatter)\n- `MEMORY.md` 索引条目\n\n**详见**：[[extractMemories_architecture.md]]","x":-600,"y":900,"width":350,"height":260,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"prompts-module","type":"text","text":"# Prompts 渲染引擎\n\n**Session Prompts**：\n- 强制骨架协议（禁改章节标题）\n- Token 字数审计（超 12K 警告）\n- 截断器 `truncateSessionMemoryForCompact`\n- 用户自定义覆写点\n\n**Extract Prompts**：\n- 两步走卡片式存储\n- 反调查指令\n- Private vs Team Memory 分家\n\n**详见**：[[prompts_architecture.md]]","x":-100,"y":1200,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"hooks-module","type":"text","text":"# Hooks 系统 - 自动化骨架\n\n**生命周期 Hooks**：\n- pre-command / post-command\n- sessionFileAccessHooks.ts\n\n**进程环境 Hooks**：\n- subprocessEnv.ts 预处理\n\n**后台触发管线**：\n- `registerPostSamplingHook` → sessionMemory\n- `handleStopHooks` → extractMemories\n\n**配置热更新**：\n- changeDetector.ts / settingsCache.ts\n\n**详见**：[[hooks_architecture.md]]","x":350,"y":1200,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"5"},
		{"id":"output","type":"text","text":"# 终端渲染输出\n\n**渲染内容**：\n- 流式逐字打印\n- 工具执行状态动画\n- 记忆保存通知 [X memories saved]\n\n**渲染宿主**：React Ink TUI","x":-60,"y":1500,"width":450,"height":160,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"design-philosophy","type":"text","text":"# 三大设计哲学\n\n## 1. 洋葱模型\n层层包裹大模型\n\n**最内层** query.ts → 直接与 API 对话\n**中间层** Tool + compact → 手脚 + 防爆\n**外围层** QueryEngine + Hooks → 生命周期\n**最外层** CLI + context → 入口 + 感知\n\n## 2. 防御性设计\n- 上下文：三级阶梯防线\n- 工具：沙盒 + 权限 + 并发安全\n- 记忆：零信任权限锁死\n- 预算：美元+Token 双限\n\n## 3. 异步影子系统\n- 记忆提取：后台 Fork\n- Prompt Cache：寄生复用\n- 60 秒宽限期：抗 Ctrl+C","x":900,"y":900,"width":400,"height":400,"color":"6"},
		{"id":"builtin-agents","type":"text","text":"# 内置 Agent 系统\n\n| Agent | subagent_type | 用途 |\n|-------|-------------|------|\n| general-purpose | - | 通用任务处理 |\n| Explore | Explore | 快速探索代码库 |\n| Plan | Plan | 架构规划与设计 |\n| verification | verification | 独立验证代码 |\n| claude-code-guide | - | 文档指南 |\n\n**Agent Teams**：\n```\nTeam Lead\n├── frontend-dev\n├── backend-dev\n└── database-dev\n```","x":500,"y":-240,"width":350,"height":260,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"skills-system","type":"text","text":"# Skills 系统\n\n**内置 Skills**：\n- /verify - 验证代码\n- /debug - 调试助手\n- /simplify - 代码简化\n- /remember - 记忆管理\n- /batch - 批量处理\n- /loop - 定时任务\n- /gsd - 高效执行框架\n\n**Skill 结构**：\n```\nskill-name/\n├── SKILL.md (required)\n└── resources/\n    ├── scripts/\n    ├── references/\n    └── assets/\n```","x":900,"y":-240,"width":350,"height":260,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"tools-list","type":"text","text":"# 核心工具清单\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| FileRead | 读取文件内容 |\n| FileWrite | 写入新文件 |\n| FileEdit | 编辑现有文件 |\n| BashTool | 执行 Shell 命令 |\n| AgentTool | 启动子 Agent |\n| MCPTool | MCP 协议工具 |\n| SkillTool | Skills 调用 |\n| Glob | 文件模式匹配 |\n| Grep | 内容搜索 |\n\n**详见**：[[Tool_architecture.md]]","x":-1550,"y":200,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"4"},
		{"id":"file-structure","type":"text","text":"# 文件结构总览\n\n```\ncc-haha-main/\n├── src/\n│   ├── entrypoints/     # CLI 入口\n│   ├── tools/           # 工具系统\n│   ├── services/        # 服务层\n│   │   ├── QueryEngine.ts\n│   │   └── MCPClient.ts\n│   ├── components/      # UI 组件\n│   ├── utils/           # 工具函数\n│   └── ink/             # 终端 UI\n├── docs/                # 文档\n└── .claude/             # 配置目录\n```","x":-1550,"y":-1000,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"config-structure","type":"text","text":"# 配置目录结构\n\n```\n~/.claude/\n├── settings.json    # 用户配置\n├── skills/          # 自定义 Skills\n├── agents/          # 自定义 Agents\n├── teams/           # Agent Teams\n├── plugins/         # 插件\n├── memory/          # 记忆系统\n│   ├── MEMORY.md\n│   └── daily/\n└── projects/        # 按项目隔离\n```","x":-1550,"y":-640,"width":350,"height":240,"color":"1"}
	],
